  "description": "You conjure spirits from the Elemental Planes that flit around you in a 15-foot Emanation for the duration. Until the spell ends, any attack you make deals an extra 2d8 damage when you hit a creature in the Emanation. This damage is Acid, Cold, Fire, or Lightning (your choice when you make the attack).\n\nIn addition, the ground in the Emanation is &amp;Reference[DifficultTerrain] for your enemies.\n\nUsing a Higher-Level Spell Slot. The damage increases by 1d8 for each spell slot level above 4.",
